Final_Rank_by_Avg_Vi_1.query: Visit = load "${App.Datasets.CG_Visit36_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; Visit_A = filter Visit by 'Status' in ["Completed","Abandonded"]; Visit_B = filter Visit by 'Status' == "Completed"; Visit_C = filter Visit by 'ActualVisitEndTime_sec_epoch' is not null; Visit_result = group Visit_A by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' full, Visit_B by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' full, Visit_C by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName'; Visit_result = foreach Visit_result generate  Visit_A.'Visitor_UniqueUserName' as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName',  first(Visit_A.'Visitor_SmallPhotoUrl') as 'Rep_Pic', count(Visit_B)/count(Visit_A) as 'Percent_of_Successful_visits',  count(Visit_B) as 'Number_of_Completed_Visits',  count(Visit_A) as 'Total_Number_of_Completed_n_Abandonded', avg(Visit_C.'ActualVisitDuration') as 'avg_ActualVisitDuration', count(Visit_A) as 'Number_of_Visits', unique(Visit_A.'ActualVisitStartTime_YearMonthDay') as 'unique_ActualVisitStartTime_YearMonthDay', count(Visit_A) / unique(Visit_A.'ActualVisitStartTime_YearMonthDay') as 'avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day'; Visit_result = group Visit_result by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName'; Visit_result = foreach Visit_result generate  'Visitor_UniqueUserName' as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName', first('Rep_Pic') as 'Rep_Pic', avg('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day') as 'avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day', dense_rank() over([..] partition by all order by avg('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day') desc) as 'Owner_Rank', avg('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day') as 'Value', avg(sum('avg_Number_of_Visits_per_Day')) over ([..] partition by all) as 'avg_All_Owners'; fake = group Visit by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName';      fake = foreach fake generate "{{cell(Visitor_UniqueUserNa_1.selection,0,"Visitor_UniqueUserName").asString()}}" as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName', 0  as 'Owner_Rank', 0 as 'Value', 0 as 'avg_All_Owners';      result_final = union Visit_result,fake;      result_final = filter result_final by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' == "{{cell(Visitor_UniqueUserNa_1.selection,0,"Visitor_UniqueUserName").asString()}}";      result_final = group result_final by 'Visitor_UniqueUserName';      result_final = foreach result_final generate 'Visitor_UniqueUserName' as 'Visitor_UniqueUserName', case when sum('Owner_Rank') == 0 then "NA" else number_to_string(sum('Owner_Rank'),"#,###") end as 'Owner_Rank', sum('Value') as 'Value of Selected_Owner', round(sum('avg_All_Owners'),2) as 'avg_All_Owners_Visits_per_Day', case when sum('Value') == 0 then "rgb(168, 183, 199)" when sum('Value') >= sum('avg_All_Owners') then       "rgb(8, 161, 50)" else "rgb(232,67,64)" end as 'Color_Top_Bottom';
